Impacted customers may see Magic Firewall rules not being applied to a small subset of packets processed in these locations since 2023-12-21 6 am UTC: Los Angeles (LAX), Dallas (DFW), Atlanta (ATL), Hong Kong (HKG), Madrid (MAD), Chicago (ORD), London (LHR), Ashburn (IAD) and Frankfurt (FRA).

We are working to mitigate impact to Magic Firewall customers. More updates to follow shortly.

incidents.name: Elevated errors for customers using Cloudflare Tunnels

incident_updates.body: This incident has been resolved.
A fix has been implemented and we are monitoring the results.
The issue has been identified and a fix is being implemented.

Cloudflare is investigating issues establishing connectivity to Cloudflare Tunnels from Brussels. Tunnels connected to these colos may experience elevated levels of 522 errors. All other colos do not appear to be impacted at this time.
